CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 16, 1947, pg. 27, reads: "Co-Workers Entertained - Miss Marjorie E. Gaines of Highland View Heights entertained some of her co-workers of the Veterans Administration at the Hermitage Street home of her grandmother, Mrs. Nannie B. Allen, last Saturday. The guests were Miss Estelle Van Duyer of California, Ruth Crouse of Ingram, Bessie Wiess of McKeesport and Helen Papariella of Pittsburgh. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Veterans Administration workers Ruth Crouse, Estelle Van Duyer, Marjorie E. Gaines, Helen Papariella, and Bessie Wiess gathered in yard of home of Nannie B. Allen, Hermitage Street
